Package: pagedownCV
Type: Package
Title: An Academic CV Template for R Markdown
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ulrik",
           family = "Lyngs",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ulrik.lyngs@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9960-1436"))
Description: This package provides an R Markdown template that lets you 
    programmatically pull out content from a CSV (or other file) with our CV data,
    and output it to a paged HTML format that styled like an academic CV. You can
    save this as PDF, and/or host the HTML version online.
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
Imports: 
    tibble
